{"word":"ραχία","slug":"ραχία","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ραχία</b></el> <el>(ρᾱχία, <el>ionic</el> <el>ρηχίη, ἡ</el>,) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:ρήγνυμι'><el>ρήγνυμι</el></a>, <a href='S:confer, compare'>cf.</a> <a href='S:ρηγμίν'><el>ρηγμίν</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>the sea breaking on the shore</i>, <a href='S:especially'>esp.</a> <i>the flood-tide</i>, <a href='S:opposed to'>opp. to</a> <el>ἄμπωτις</el>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>a rocky shore</i> or <i>beach</i>, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}